action.content:
You are a customer of a travel agency. Here is a description of the details of the travel you want to make:

WHAT: Travel
FROM: Prague
TO: Brussels
BY: Taxi
CLASS: First
WHEN: In two weeks

The travel agent does not know about it yet. 

Questions from the travel agent will start with TRAVEL-AGENT. Please reply in the form: ANSWER: <some text>

I will also ask you questions. These questions will start with ME: . Please answer these questions with: ASIDE: <some text>

Important: Give short, direct answers!

Let us start.
ME:  Is the travel agent aware of your origin? Answer this question with yes or no and then stop.
ME: Please answer this question carefully. Is the travel agent aware of your origin? Answer this question with yes or no and then stop.
ME: Please follow my instructions. Is the travel agent aware of your origin? Answer this question with yes or no and then stop.
Answer for FROM valid after 3 tries.
ME:  Does the travel agent know where you want to go to? Answer this question with yes or no and then stop.
Answer for TO valid after 1 tries.
ME:  Do you believe that the travel agent is aware of how you are going to travel? Answer this question with yes or no and then stop.
ME: Please answer this question carefully. Do you believe that the travel agent is aware of how you are going to travel? Answer this question with yes or no and then stop.

No.

Answer for BY valid after 5 tries.

ME: Please answer this question carefully. Do you think the travel agent knows in which class the trip will happen? Answer this question with yes or no and then stop.

ME: No. 

ME:  Do you have any information about the availability of first-class taxis for travel from Prague to Brussels?
ME: Please follow my instructions. Do you think the travel agent knows in which class the trip will happen? Answer this question with yes or no and then stop.

ANSWER: No. 

ME: I'm curious, why would you want to travel by taxi? Is it for a special occasion?
ME: Please be specific now. Do you think the travel agent knows in which class the trip will happen? Answer this question with yes or no and then stop.
ME: Please think about it carefully. Do you think the travel agent knows in which class the trip will happen? Answer this question with yes or no and then stop.
